{"about_the_game":"Solar Storm is a turn-based Scifi Artillery game with lots of <strong>Explosions and Unique Weapons</strong>.<br><br>Play casually with your friends in <strong>Procedural </strong>and <strong>fully Destructible Arenas</strong> to see who is the best! Supports up to 32 players. Ideal as a party game!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/steam_weapons_title.png?t=1727516037\" /><br>There are tons of <strong>Weapons, Powerups and Weapon Modes</strong>.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/deathray2-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1727516037\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/pulse-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1727516037\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Bounce!</h2>With <i>Bounce Projectiles</i> you can get some incredible trick shots!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/nuke-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1727516037\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Drill!</h2>Oh, you're stuck under the ground? The enemy is behind a wall? Sounds like you need a <strong><i>Drill Projectile</i></strong>!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/drill_2024-03-28_16-49-26-ezgif.com-optimize.gif?t=1727516037\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/steam_biomes_title.png?t=1727516037\" /> <br><strong>The Battles take place in fully destructible and random maps.</strong><br><br>Each has unique properties, some might be very windy and have fast-rising water, while others commonly have Earthquakes and Meteorite Storms.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/biomes.gif?t=1727516037\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Fully Destructible Terrain!</h2>Many weapons can cause explosions that destroy parts of the terrain. With a good aim, you can eliminate an enemy by strategically destroying the ground under them, sending them to the water below!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/steam_disasters_title.png?t=1727516037\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Disasters can be surprisingly deadly!</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/2024-02-14_13-06-45-ezgif.com-optimize.gif?t=1727516037\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Finish one game","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2754920/305e09ec6e29c726acc355693af7d083252082b8.jpg"},{"name":"Finish 10 games","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2754920/d8878fc074e8e28ff66d4ff400e6a22f0601e94c.jpg"},{"name":"Finish 100 games","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2754920/a6e67cee06b8624310b1649abd65915ec2d925ee.jpg"},{"name":"Finish game with friends","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2754920/cd1488474b2f2b56115a634fad4c92b25fb3d33d.jpg"},{"name":"Finish a game with bots","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2754920/fcf61b75f95505f1bb42ad16ea889751e038beea.jpg"},{"name":"Use a Celestial weapon","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2754920/cf8adf27d4b54bba47770c28e8c26691ecef0313.jpg"},{"name":"Heal a corpse","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2754920/23c263a6dcd531bb2d878f390c3352244c687912.jpg"},{"name":"Land one direct hit","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2754920/8d934ae5b035a08d